title: Pokemon Movie 10 - The Rise of Darkrai (Standard Quality)
description:
This is Pokemon Movie 10, entitled "The Rise of Darkrai", which was aired 2/24/08 on Cartoon Network. The movie has not yet been released on DVD, so this is a capture from the airing.

This is in WMV format and this is the Standard version of the film (It\&#039;s under 700 MBs, standard size for most PCs and Media Centers). All commercials have been removed and the movie re-spliced together to the best of my abilities using Windows Movie Maker. 

I&#039;m working on DivX encoding now, and will offer up DivX encodings for people later once it&#039;s done. 

Until then, enjoy! ^______^
